{
  "stem": "10768.5",
  "chunk_idx": 0,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 3.4,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "We were staying in Biesenthal for about six weeks or maybe two months.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Berlin was already at that time taken over by the Russian army and by the Polish army.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And we ourselves, from the hospital, since the hospital didn't have already too many sick people, we took sort of a ride into Berlin in May 7 or 8, approximately, 1945.",
      "word_count": 31
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "We came to Berlin when the Reichstag was burning, and we came to the Kaiser Wilhelm Monument.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "We saw a lot of Russians who came there at the same time.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And this was just the good feeling that we had some accomplishment, some input into the, the destruction or the defeat of the German army.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "In Biesenthal, that city, we were there another-- probably May until the end of June.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "In June, our hospital was evacuated, sort of to say.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "The sick people were not there anymore, but we went back on a territory, which was, before the war, a German city.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "It was called Rokitnica.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And our hospital was told to establish there.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "We were already in buildings.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "At that time, of course, I had a room with a shower.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "And at that time, I started to look for my brother.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "And through every sick person who was coming, first I was looking if it's not my brother himself because I looked at the faces.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "And then whoever came, I was finding out, and somehow-- I don't remember the details how I found out to where my brother was.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "He was in the Second Army, and he was southern-- that he was sent to the southern part, through Breslau into, I think, Dresden.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "And a few days before the war ended, he was injured.",
      "word_count": 11
    }
  ],
